0Combs'%20lead%20lawyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20going%20to%20say%20slippery%20slope%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawyer%2C%20Marc%20Agnifilo%2C%20joked%20after%20the%20judge%20said%20prosecutors%20might%20be%20nearing%20the%20point%20of%20overkill%20on%20the%20topic.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I'm%20not%20going%20to%20say%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20defense%20objection%20and%20sidebar%20discussion%20briefly%20interrupted%20Ventura's%20first%20day%20of%20testimony%20at%20Combs'%20federal%20racketeering%20and%20sex%20trafficking%20trial%20in%20Manhattan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20are%20using%20Ventura's%20very%20detailed%20testimony%20about%20baby%20oil%2C%20drugs%2C%20lubricants%2C%20candles%2C%20and%20other%20alleged%20freak%20off%20supplies%20to%20bolster%20the%20charge%20that%20Combs%20personally%20%26quot%3Borchestrated%26quot%3B%20these%20elaborately-planned%2C%20dayslong%20sex%20performances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECombs%20demanded%20that%20heated%20Johnson's%20baby%20oil%20be%20available%20in%20large%20quantities%20for%20the%20nearly%20weekly%20encounters%2C%20during%20which%20he%20would%20film%20male%20escorts%20and%20strippers%20having%20sex%20with%20Ventura%2C%20according%20to%20her%20testimony%20and%20the%20indictment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20replied%20when%20prosecutor%20Emily%20A.%20Johnson%20asked%20who%20would%20apply%20the%20oil.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20need%20to%20be%20glistening%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20Combs%20would%20repeatedly%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20defense%20objection%20was%20raised%20after%20Ventura%20described%20a%20freak%20off%20she%20said%20happened%20at%20the%20L'Ermitage%20hotel%20in%20Beverly%20Hills.%20Combs%20demanded%20that%20a%20blow-up%20pool%20be%20brought%20to%20their%20hotel%20suite%20there%2C%20and%20that%20it%20be%20%26quot%3Bfilled%20with%20lube%20and%20oil%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20jurors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDid%20you%20get%20into%20the%20pool%3F%26quot%3B%20Jo