20companies%20should%20focus%20on%20using%20AI%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-will-change-most-jobs-employers-help-workers-keep-up-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereskill%20rather%20than%20replace%3C%2Fa%3E%20them.%20With%20so%20much%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-tools-reality-vs-hype-letdown-big-tech-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehype%20around%20AI-powered%20tools%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Fleming%20said%20companies%20should%20be%20intentional%20about%20treating%20AI%20as%20a%20collaborator%2C%20not%20a%20substitute%20for%20humans.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20important%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20partnership.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20experimentation%20and%20exploration%20are%20key%20to%20building%20that%20partnership.%20BI%20spoke%20with%20Fleming%20about%20how%20businesses%20can%20put%20that%20into%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20clarity%20and%20length.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAs%20AI%20becomes%20more%20embedded%20in%20companies%2C%20you%20say%20that%20employers%20should%20focus%20on%20upskilling%20rather%20than%20cutting%20costs.%20Why%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%20and%20foremost%2C%20it%20makes%20for%20better%20products.%20A%20lot%20of%20companies%20are%20focused%20on%20being%20%26quot%3BAI%20first%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20often%20the%20best%20solutions%20are%20human-driven%20or%20involve%20other%20types%20of%20problem-solving.%20Whether%20you're%20making%20products%20or%20changing%20work%20processes%2C%20it's%20about%20balance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20you%20think%20companies%20sometimes%20miss%20the%20mark%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20how%20they%20integrate%20AI%20into%20work%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20talked%20to%20someone%20recently%20who's%20thinking%20of%20starting%20a%20company.%20He%20asked%20me%2C%20%26quot%3BHow%20can%20we%20use%20AI%20to%20help%20people%20work%20better%3F%26quot%3B%20I%20said%20that%20while%20AI%20can%20definitely%20improve%20efficiency%2C%20the%20first%20step%20is%20understanding%20what%20people%20actually%20do%2C%20the%20problems%20they%20face%2C%20and%20what%20they%20need%20help%20with.%20There%20are%20aspects%20of%20work%20people%20enjoy%20and%20find%20rewarding%20%E2%80%94%20those%20are%20areas%20where%20AI%20shouldn't%20intervene.%20People%20want%20their%20work%20to%20feel%20meaningful.%20It's%20not%20just%20about%20adding%20AI%2C%20but%20making%20sure%20it%20supports%20the%20right%20aspects%20of%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22764%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chelsey%20Fleming%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67eed82663d72727e19921f0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22573%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChelsey%20Fleming%20is%20a%20user%20experience%20research%20lead%20at%20Google%20Labs.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Irina%20Logra%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThere's%20evidence%20that%20many%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-get-employees-to-use-ai-at-work-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3Eemployees%20are%20reluctant%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%2C%20and%20even%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-adoption-worker-survey-big-tech-spending-2025%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3Eresistant%2C%20to%20using%20AI%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E.%20Why%20do%20you%20think%20that%20is%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20feel%20overwhelmed%20by%20the%20sheer%20number%20of%20AI%20tools%20out%20there%20and%20by%20the%20thought%20of%20having%20to%20learn%20them.%20I%20get%20that.%20It's%20hard%20to%20know%20where%20to%20start.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20when%20companies%20treat%20AI%20training%20as%20a%20requirement%2C%20it%20can%20feel%20like%20a%20chore.%20If%20you're%20thinking%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20to%20learn%20this%20for%20my%20job%2C%26quot%3B%20it's%20a%20burden.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%2C%20how%20can%20companies%20make%20using%20AI%20and%20upskilling%20more%20engaging%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20people%20are%20given%20room%20to%20experiment%20with%20new%20tools%2C%20it%20becomes%20much%20more%20engaging.%20On%20my%20team%2C%20we%20had%20a%20series%20of%20Friday%20workshops%20where%20we%20could%20explore%20AI%3A%20prototyping%20and%20testing%20things%20out.%20It%20made%20all%20the%20difference.%20If%20companies%20want%20people%20to%20learn%2C%20they%20should%20make%20it%20enjoyable%20by%20carving%20out%20small%20amounts%20of%20time%20for%20experimentation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20should%20a%20company%20measure%20the%20ROI%20of%20that%20exploration%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wouldn't%20necessarily%20try%20to%20quantify%20experimentation%3B%20that's%20the%20point%20of%20experimenting.%20Sometimes%20you'll%20realize%20a%20tool%20isn't%20useful%2C%20and%20that's%20a%20great%20learning%20outcome.%20If%20you%20figure%20out%20it's%20not%20going%20to%20work%20for%20you%2C%20fantastic%20%E2%80%94%20you%20can%20move%20on%20and%20focus%20on%20something%20that%20does.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20develop%20these%20tools%2C%20we%20try%20to%20anticipate%20every%20possible%20use%20case%2C%20but%20once%20they're%20out%20in%20the%20world%2C%20people%20come%20up%20with%20things%20we%20never%20expected.%20That's%20part%20of%20the%20joy.%20But%20if%20you%20don't%20have%20a%20healthy%20mindset%20around%20experimentation%20and%20adaptation%2C%20people%20won't%20discover%20unexpected%20ways%20to%20apply%20the%20tool.%20They'll%20only%20see%20what's%20right%20in%20front%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20your%20line%20of%20work%2C%20do%20you%20think%20there%20will%20always%20need%20to%20be%20a%20human%20in%20the%20loop%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20applications%20are%20powerful%20for%20accele