erospace%20as%20just%20the%20beginning%20of%20AR%2FVR%20collaboration.%20Unlike%20many%20of%20Campfire's%20competitors%2C%20which%20often%20target%20narrow%20use%20cases%2C%20Wright%20hopes%20to%20make%20AR%2FVR%20collaboration%20as%20popular%20and%20accessible%20as%20videoconferencing%20platforms%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-zoom-main-meeting-app-microsoft-365-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EZoom%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20can%20just%20start.%20They%20can%20download%20something%20for%20free%2C%20and%20then%20they%20can%20upgrade%20to%20a%20paid%20plan%20when%20they%20feel%20they've%20exhausted%20the%20features%20of%20what's%20free%2C%26quot%3B%20Wright%20said.%20%26quot%3BJust%20like%20a%20Zoom%2C%20a%20Teams%2C%20a%20Slack%2C%20a%20Miro%2C%20a%20Figma.%20That's%20the%20exact%20same%20thing%20with%20Campfire.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221290%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jay%20Wright%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68234f4f3fe8d3928365abf7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22968%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJay%20Wright%20is%20the%20CEO%20of%20Campfire.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Campfire%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229fb96aad-11cf-4aa8-a7f6-59b5d3e61e25%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETaking%20AR%2FVR%20collaboration%20mainstream%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20adoption%20of%20AR%2FVR%20collaboration%20has%20been%20slow%20in%20part%20because%20most%20tools%20are%20difficult%20to%20download%20and%20use.%20Many%20lack%20a%20free%20trial%2C%20or%20if%20one%20is%20offered%2C%20it%20may%20only%20be%20available%20for%20a%20limited%20time.%20Hardware%20requirements%2C%20like%20a%20headset%20or%20a%20powerful%20computer%2C%20and%20device%20compatibility%20are%20additional%20obstacles.%20This%20can%20raise%20barriers%20for%20companies%20and%20individuals%20looking%20to%20explore%20the%20tech%20before%20making%20a%20full%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20many%20AR%2FVR%20collaboration%20apps%2C%20Campfire%20is%20designed%20for%203D%2C%20real-time%20collaboration%20in%20an%20AR%2FVR%20environment.%20Users%20can%20load%203D%20files%20and%20view%20them%20at%20an%20accurate%20scale%2C%20zoom%20in%20and%20out%20to%20see%20components%20in%20more%20detail%2C%20and%20make%20alterations%20on%20the%20fly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20unlike%20most%20competitors%2C%20Campfire%20also%20provides%20a%20comprehensive%20free%20tier.%20Under%20this%20plan%2C%20users%20can%20view%20up%20to%20five%20projects%20with%20up%20to%20five%20collaborators%20and%20receive%205GB%20of%20total%20file%20storage.%20The%20free%20tier%20has%20no%20time%20limits.%20Campfire%20also%20offers%20broad%20device%20compatibility%2C%20including%20Windows%2C%20Mac%2C%20Varjo%20headsets%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20model%20similar%20to%20other%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fsaas%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esoftware-as-a-service%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20people%20can%20download%20something%20for%20free%2C%26quot%3B%20Wright%20said.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20can%20use%20models%20up%20to%20a%20certain%20size%2C%20in%20certain%20formats%2C%20and%20it's%20really%20good.%20They%20can%20see%20what%20the%20collaboration%20experience%20looks%20like%2C%20they%20can%20put%20their%20own%20data%20in.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20the%20recent%20release%20of%20more%20affordable%20and%20accessible%20headsets%2C%20like%20Meta's%20Quest%203%2C%20flexibility%20is%20key%20to%20the%20company's%20strategy.%20Wright%20said%20roughly%2080%25%20of%20Campfire's%20users%20log%20in%20through%20a%20computer%2C%20tablet%2C%20or%20phone.%20If%20collaborators%20on%20a%20project%20lack%20a%20headset%2C%20they%20can%20still%20use%20a%20laptop%20to%20view%20the%20perspective%20of%20a%20team%20member%20who's%20wearing%20the%20device.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222763%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Thomas%20Murphy%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6823855e3fe8d3928365b886%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223597%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThomas%20Murphy%20is%20a%20manufacturing%20programs%20chief%20engineer%20at%20Collins%20Aerospace.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Thomas%20Murphy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ce755729-afda-4abb-97e4-50abad6817b8%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFrom%20ideation%20to%20the%20air%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECollins%20Aerospace%2C%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20RTX%2C%20builds%20components%20for%20commercial%20and%20defense%20aviation%2C%20from%20navigation%20equipment%20and%20landing%20gear%20to%20passenger%20seats.%20The%20company%20began%20using%20Campfire%20in%202023.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMurphy%20told%20BI%20he%20sees%20an%20opportunity%20for%20the%20tech%20to%20reinvent%20the%20company's%20complicated%20review%20process.%20Collaborators%20typically%20view%20the%203D%20models%2C%20take%20detailed%20notes%2C%20create%20action%20items%2C%20make%20changes%2C%20reconvene%20to%20discuss%20the%20updates%2C%20and%20repeat%20until%20they%20finalize%20the%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20design%20reviews%2C%20and%20we're%20pasting%203D%20models%20into%20two-dimensional%20PowerPoint%20slides%20and%20going%20through%20those%20cross-sectional%20views%20on%20a%20Zoom%20call%2C%26quot%3B%20Murphy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECampfire%2C%20by%20contrast%2C%20allows%20direct%20and%20real-time%20collaboration.%20Murphy%20said%20users%20can%20view%203D%20CAD%20files%20that%20offer%20a%20much%20clearer%20representation%20of%20what%20a%20final%20product%20will%20look%20like.%20Collaborators%20can%20also%20alter%20the%20file%20in%20real%20time%2C%20making%20it%20possible%20to%20share%20iterations%20on%20the%20spot%20and%20experiment%20with%20new%20ideas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20aerospace%20industry's%20demanding%20timelines%20make%20speedy%20collaboration%20particularly%20valuable.%20Murphy%20said%20that%20Collins%20Aerospace%20needs%20to%20move%20in%20step%20with%20major%20customers.%20%26quot%3BFrom%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboeing-f47-fighter-jet-plane-orders-777x-turnaround-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBoeing%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairbus-sketches-next-plane-folding-wings-radical-new-engines-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAirbus%3C%2Fa%3E%20perspective%2C%20they're%20looking%20for%20us%20to%20have%20the%20agility%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20tech%20has%20been%20used%20successfully%20at%20Collins%20Aerospace%20and%20companies%20like%20DataFusion%20and%20Whirlpool%2C%20Campfire%20could%20face%20potential%20adoption%20hurdles%20as%20tech%20giants%20remain%20undecided%20about%20AR%2FVR%20technology.%20Microsoft%2C%20for%20example%2C%20has%20largely%20retreated%20from%20Windows%20Mixed%20Reality%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-hololens-3-metaverse-mixed-reality-strategy-confusion-rivalries-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHoloLens%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20holographic%20headset%20it%20once%20pitched%20to%20engineers%2C%20and%20Meta's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-q1-2025-earnings-reality-labs-layoffs-losses-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EReality%20Labs%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20a%20%244.2%20billion%20loss%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20Wright%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20time%20is%20right%20for%20AR%2FVR%20collaboration%20to%20go%20mainstream.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverything%20is%20not%20obvious%20until%20the%20moment%20that%20it's%20very%20obvious%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20promise%20has%20been%20there%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20and%20it's%20just%20a%20matter%20of%20getting%20to%20that%20tipping%20point%20where%20you've%20got%20p