ame%20to%20Max%2C%20which%20it's%20now%20ditching.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20if%20you%20think%20that's%20a%20pretty%20funny%20example%20of%20sweaty%20corporate%20pivoting%20and%20flailing%20%E2%80%94%20the%20kind%20of%20stuff%20that%20regularly%20got%20flayed%20on%20HBO's%20%26quot%3BSuccession%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20you%20are%20not%20alone.%20The%20folks%20at%20WBD%20also%20acknowledge%20the%20silliness%20of%20the%20whole%20episode%2C%20and%20are%20distributing%20a%20mea%20culpa%20meme%20to%20poke%20fun%20at%20themselves%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Friends%20meme%20announcing%20change%20from%20Max%20to%20HBO%20Max%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68249a723fe8d3928365cb68%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETurning%20HBO%20into%20HBO%20Max%20and%20then%20Max%20and%20now%20HBO%20Max%20is%20pretty%20funny%20%E2%80%94%20something%20the%20streaming%20service%20is%20acknowledging%20itself%20by%20distributing%20this%20meme%20to%20the%20media.%3Cp%3EWarner%20Bros.%20Discovery%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20that's%20the%20fun%20part.%20There%20is%20some%20more%20serious%20stuff%20going%20on%20behind%20the%20scenes%2C%20though.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20starters%2C%20this%20is%20yet%20another%20acknowledgment%20that%20the%20thesis%20behind%20the%20merger%20of%20what%20used%20to%20be%20called%20WarnerMedia%20and%20Discovery%20hasn't%20panned%20out.%20The%20thesis%20was%20that%20combining%20HBO's%20programming%20with%20reality%20TV%20programming%20would%20make%20a%20streaming%20service%20with%20broad%20enough%20appeal%20to%20take%20on%20Netflix.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20that%20the%20WBD%20folks%20are%20saying%20that%20exactly%20in%20public.%20But%20you%20can%20read%20between%20the%20lines%20in%20the%20press%20release%20announcing%20the%20change%2C%20where%20the%20company%20says%20its%20streaming%20service%20is%20thriving%20because%20of%20%26quot%3