2F08%2Fcoffee-sandwiches-underwear-beer-day-in-the-life-japan-konbini-stores%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20offer%20a%20huge%20variety%20of%20items%2C%20from%20underwear%20to%20face%20masks%20to%20alcohol.%20It's%20the%20wealth%20of%20fresh%2C%20prepared%20foods%20that%20sets%20them%20apart%20from%20their%20US%20counterparts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIt%20was%20around%2010%20a.m.%20on%20a%20Sunday%2C%20and%20the%20egg%20sandwiches%20were%20nearly%20all%20gone%20from%20the%20shelves.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Four%20sandwiches%20wrapped%20in%20plastic%20on%20a%20white%20shelf%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682398d8c6ad288d1480d204%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPotato%20salad%20sandwiches%20didn't%20seem%20quite%20as%20popular%20as%20the%20egg%20ones.%3Cp%3EJenny%20McGrath%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20plenty%20of%20potato%20salad%20options%20left%2C%20though.%20Tuna%20and%20egg%20and%20ham%20and%20egg%20options%20were%20also%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20sandwich%20expired%20two%20days%20after%20I%20bought%20it%2C%20at%2011%20p.m.%2C%20according%20to%20its%20label.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMilk%20bread%20and%20Kewpie%20mayo%20are%20the%20keys%20to%20a%20great%20egg%20sandwich.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20nutrition%20label%20on%20a%20packaged%20sandwich%20in%20Japanese%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68239b723fe8d3928365bcb4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20label%20on%20the%20Lawson%20egg%20sandwich%20gave%20an%20expiration%20date%20with%20the%20hour.%3Cp%3EJenny%20McGrath%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFluffy%20and%20lightly%20flavored%2C%20milk%20bread%2C%20or%20shokupan%2C%20adds%20a%20touch%20of%20sweetness.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bonappetit.com%2Fstory%2Fmilk-bread-obsession%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBon%20App%C3%A9tit%3C%2Fa%3E%20compared%20its%20softness%20to%20white%20bread%20but%20with%20more%20fat.%20The%20sandwiches%20are%20crustless%2C%20cut%20into%20perfect%20squishy%20triangles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20trying%20to%20replicate%20the%20sandwich%20in%20the%20US%20typically%20use%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhich-brand-best-mayonnaise-at-grocery-store-review-mayo-ranking%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKewpie%20mayo%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20Japanese%20brand%20uses%20an%20extra%20egg%20yolk%2C%20several%20types%20of%20vinegar%2C%20and%20MSG%2C%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tastingtable.com%2F731214%2Fis-there-a-difference-between-kewpie-mayo-and-regular%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETasting%20Table%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20result%20is%20a%20creamy%2C%20rich%20sauce%20that's%20a%20little%20different%20from%20other%20types%20of%20mayo%2C%20though%20the%20US%20version%20doesn't%20contain%20MSG.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20paired%20it%20with%20a%20caf%C3%A9%20au%20lait%20and%20bottled%20water%2C%20all%20for%20under%20%244.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shelves%20filled%20with%20to-go%20cups%20of%20coffee%20and%20other%20beverages%20with%20Japanese%20writing%20on%20them%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682397f6c6ad288d1480d1d8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJapan's%20convenience%20stores%20have%20countless%20beverage%20choices.%3Cp%3EJenny%20McGrath%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20shortage%20of%20canned%20coffees%20and%20other%20beverages%20available%20in%20to-go%20cups.%20The%20latter%20came%20with%20straws%20to%20pierce%20through%20the%20foil%20tops.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20buying%20my%20items%2C%20I%20tasted%20the%20sandwich.%20The%20bread%20was%20soft%20and%20springy%2C%20while%20the%20filling%20was%20rich%20with%20a%20touch%20of%20tanginess.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20got%20back%20to%20the%20US%2C%20I%20checked%20out%20the%20sandwich%20options%20in%20my%20local%207-Eleven.%20There%20was%20a%20small%20cooler%20with%20a%20few%20options%2C%20including%20an%20egg%20salad.%20It%20cost%20%245.29%2C%20more%20than%20double%20what%20I%20paid%20in%20Tokyo.%20Since%20its%20%26quot%3Bbest%20by%26quot%3B%20date%20was%20the%20same%20day%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20skip%20trying%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIt%20wasn't%20my%20favorite%20tamago%20sando%20I%20had%20in%20Japan%2C%20but%20I'd%20definitely%20eat%20one%20again.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20egg%20sandwich%20with%20half%20on%20top%20with%20a%20bite%20missing%20on%20a%20wooden%20desk%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682396423fe8d3928365bb88%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOne%20of%20the%20least%20expensive%20meals%20I%20had%20in%20Japan%20was%20this%20%242%20egg%20sandwich.%3Cp%3EJenny%20McGrath%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Kyoto%2C%20I%20usually%20spent%20breakfast%20at%20sit-down%20restaurants%20that%20invariably%20had%20incredible%2C%20creamy%20egg%20sandwiches%20and%20perfectly%20brewed%20coffee.%20I%20was%20able%20to%20enjoy%20a%20leisurely%20meal%20while%20planning%20out%20my%20agenda%20for%20a%20day%20of%20sightseeing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you're%20late%20for%20work%20or%20rushing%20to%20the%20airport%2C%20though%2C%20stores%20like%207-Eleven%20and%20Lawson%20can't%20be%20beat%20for%20a%20speedy%2C%20inexpensive%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjapan-egg-sandwich-convenience-store-lawson