26quot%3B%20said%20Jeff%20Buchbinder%2C%20the%20chief%20equity%20strategist%20for%20LPL%20Financial%2C%20in%20an%20email%20on%20Monday%20about%20the%20temporary%20US-China%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%2C%20rightly%20or%20wrongly%2C%20don't%20seem%20to%20be%20pricing%20in%20such%20a%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20this%20rally%20is%20just%20too%20much%20too%20fast%20until%20we%20get%20more%20specificity%20as%20far%20as%20what%20the%20real%20trade%20terms%20are%20going%20to%20be%2C%20what%20they%20may%20have%20as%20far%20as%20impacts%20on%20the%20economy%20overall%2C%20as%20well%20as%20what%20individual%20companies%20will%20be%20affected%20and%20which%20ones%20aren't%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dave%20Sekera%2C%20Morningstar's%20chief%20strategist%2C%20in%20a%20note%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlenty%20of%20risks%20aside%20from%20tariffs%20remain%20as%20well%2C%20like%20the%20debt%20ceiling%2C%20how%20potential%20tax%20cuts%20play%20out%2C%20and%20whether%20geopolitical%20tensions%20cool%20or%20worsen%2C%20said%20Scott%20Clemons%2C%20chief%20investment%20strategist%20at%20Brown%20Brothers%20Harriman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClemons%20told%20Business%20Insider%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20while%20recession%20clouds%20are%20starting%20to%20clear%20with%20the%20trade%20outlook%20improving%2C%20the%20recent%20spell%20of%20volatility%20in%20financial%20markets%20probably%20isn't%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20we're%20out%20of%20the%20woods%20yet%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20volatility%2C%26quot%3B%20Clemons%20said.%20%26quot%3BEven%20yesterday%20talking%20to%20clients%20after%20the%20relief%20rally%3A%20'Oh%20my%20god%2C%20thank%20the%20whole%20tariff%20thing%20is%20over.'%20I'm%20like%2C%20'Keep%20your%20seatbelts%20on%20until%20the%20ride%20comes%20to%20a%20stop.'%20And%20we're%20not%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-trade-war-china-stock-mar