2Findia%2Findian-slums-get-cool-roofs-combat-extreme-heat-2025-03-10%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20global%20trial%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20the%20Cool%20Roofs%20Programme%20is%20underway%20%E2%80%94%20India%E2%80%99s%20Ahmedabad%20stands%20out%20as%20one%20of%20the%20key%20pilot%20cities%20testing%20its%20impact%20firsthand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20initiative%20explores%20not%20just%20the%20temperature-lowering%20effects%20of%20cool%20roofs%2C%20but%20also%20their%20broader%20social%20and%20environmental%20impact%20on%20residents.%20Early%20findings%20from%20the%20trial%20suggest%20a%20promising%20reduction%20in%20indoor%20temperatures%20and%20potential%20improvements%20in%20health%20and%20living%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CSolar%20Reflective%20White%20Paint%20is%20not%20a%20normal%20paint%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fem%3Eexplains%20Dipika%20Vadgama%2C%20Programme%20Manager%20at%20Mahila%20Housing%20Trust.%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CIts%20specialised%20ingredients%20reflect%20sunlight%20rather%20than%20absorbing%20it.%20When%20the%20sun%20rays%20hit%20the%20white%20surface%2C%20they%20quickly%20bounce%20back%20instead%20of%20transferring%20heat%20inside%20the%20house.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20coats%20of%20paint%20are%20to%20be%20applied%20for%20better%20results.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20application%20process%20must%20be%20done%20with%20precision%2C%E2%80%9D%20notes%20Vadgama.%20%E2%80%9CFirst%2C%20we%20apply%20one%20layer%20of%20paint%20and%20allow%20it%20to%20dry%20for%202%20hours.%20Then%2C%20we%20apply%20a%20second%20layer%E2%80%94the%20first%20coat%20vertically%20and%20the%20second%20horizontally%E2%80%94to%20ensure%20complete%20coverage%20and%20max