967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESaves%20energy%20costs%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECool%20roofs%20also%20reduce%20the%20use%20of%20mechanical%20air%20conditioning%2C%20resulting%20in%20significant%20savings%20in%20energy%20costs%2C%20considering%20the%20rising%20demand%20for%20power%20and%20the%20stress%20it%20exerts%20on%20the%20existing%20power%20infrastructure.%20Cool%20roofs%20are%20also%20an%20excellent%20solution%20for%20reducing%20the%20urban%20heat%20island%20effect%2C%20a%20phenomenon%20in%20which%20cities%20trap%20heat%20and%20become%20excessively%20hot%20due%20to%20their%20concrete%20construction.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Cool%20roofs%20reflect%20heat%2C%20dropping%20indoor%20temps%20by%203%E2%80%936%C2%B0C%E2%80%94especially%20vital%20for%20women%20working%20from%20home.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flh7-rt.googleusercontent.com%2Fdocsz%2FAD_4nXeHZr9g0fUZB8jI_aYB0P4KG_aaSHQhB3-C-a0JXKbOQRM6fHTc52mv6Fq6AvhKqvOX1bjjQYuW3aQaANW-NzmAJ_55G9lghcyDtHFkkBGSxXDyqArIt0bTnk-huL92lJovUMnc%3Fkey%3D90kFpXKoXODW0WkgK8TZsb9f%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ECool%20roofs%20reflect%20heat%2C%20dropping%20indoor%20temps%20by%203%E2%80%936%C2%B0C%E2%80%94especially%20vital%20for%20women%20working%20from%20home.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECool%20Roofs%20Programme%20in%20India%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERoofs%20painted%20with%20white%20paint%20are%20now%20becoming%20a%20common%20sight%20in%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGujarat%20and%20Telangana%20were%20the%20first%20states%20in%20India%20to%20design%20and%20implement%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcoolroofs.org%2Fdocuments%2F2023-CRRC-Annual-Meeting-Charlotte-Steiner.pdf%5C%22%3Epilot%20program%20for%20cool%20roofs.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Ahmedabad%20Municipal%20Corporation%20and%20Hyderabad%20Municipal%20Corporation%20led%20the%20implementation%20in%20Ahmedabad%20and%20Hyderabad%2C%20respectively.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pilot%20was%20supported%20by%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nrdc.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Natural%20Resources%20Defense%20(NRDC)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20US-based%20environmental%20advocacy%20group%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mahilahousingtrust.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMahila%20Housing%20Trust%20(MHT)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20grassroots%20NGO%20in%20India.%20This%20pilot%20achieved%20a%20reduction%20of%20close%20to%203%20degrees%20in%20indoor%20temperature%20of%20houses%20painted%20with%20solar%20reflective%20paint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20in%202021%2C%20a%20new%20pilot%20programme%20was%20initiated%20in%20four%20Indian%20cities%3A%20Jodhpur%2C%20Bhopal%2C%20Surat%2C%20and%20Ahmedabad.%20The%20initiative%20was%20once%20again%20supported%20by%20the%20Natural%20Resources%20Defense%20Council%20(NRDC)%20and%20the%20Mahila%20Housing%20Trust%20(MHT)%2C%20both%20of%20which%20had%20previously%20collaborated%20on%20similar%20efforts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20pilot%20aimed%20to%20improve%20thermal%20comfort%20and%20reduce%20energy%20consumption%20in%20low-income%20households%20through%20simple%2C%20cost-effective%20interventions.%20One%20of%20the%20key%20components%20involved%20applying%20solar%20reflective%20paint%20to%20the%20roofs%20of%20houses%2C%20which%20led%20to%20a%20noticeable%20reduction%20in%20indoor%20temperatures%2C%20ranging%20between%202%20to%205%20degrees%20Celsius%2C%20providing%20much-needed%20relief%20during%20the%20hot%20months.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20the%20programme%20also%20facilitated%20the%20replacement%20of%20conventional%20incandescent%20bulbs%20with%20energy-efficient%20LED%20bulbs.%20This%20change%20contributed%20to%20lowering%20electricity%20bills%20for%20participating%20households%20and%20promoting%20long-term%20energy%20conservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20white%20roofs%20served%20as%20a%20climate-resilient%20intervention%20and%20a%20powerful%20outreach%20tool%20to%20sensitise%20and%20engage%20communities.%20Since%20its%20launch%2C%20the%20programme%20has%20turned%20over%20460%20rooftops%20white%E2%80%94impacting%20nearly%2068%2C000%20people%20across%20four%20cities%20with%20a%20simple%20coat%20of%20paint%20and%20a%20powerful%20promise%20of%20relief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETrial%20underway%20in%20Burkina%20Faso%2C%20Mexico%2C%20the%20South%20Pacific%2C%20and%20India%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20years%20later%2C%20in%202023%2C%20the%20UK-based%20Wellcome%20Trust%20launched%20a%20global%20scientific%20trial%20to%20evaluate%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20cool%20roofs%20in%20mitigating%20extreme%20heat.%20This%20large-scale%20study%20is%20being%20carried%20out%20across%20four%20countries%E2%80%94Burkina%20Faso%2C%20Mexico%2C%20the%20South%20Pacific%2C%20and%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20focus%20is%20on%20low-income%20areas%2C%20particularly%20homes%20with%20poor%20ventilation%20and%20tin%20roofs%2C%20typically%20occupied%20by%20communities%20with%20limited%20access%20to%20essential%20resources%20such%20as%20electricity%2C%20clean%20water%2C%20and%20healthcare.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20homes%20are%20highly%20vulnerable%20to%20the%20adverse%20effects%20of%20rising%20temperatures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20the%20trial%20is%20currently%20underway%20in%20the%20Vanzara%20Vas%20slum%2C%20located%20in%20the%20Narol%20area%20of%20Ahmedabad.%20As%20part%20of%20the%20study%2C%20the%20roofs%20of%20400%20homes%20are%20being%20coated%20with%20white%2C%20solar-reflective%20paint.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20results%20from%20India%20are%20still%20pending%2C%20preliminary%20findings%20from%20the%20trial%20in%20Burkina%20Faso%20are%20promising.%20Over%20a%20two-year%20period%2C%20homes%20with%20tin%20roofs%20experienced%20an%20average%20temperature%20reduction%20of%201.7%20degrees%20Celsius.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ahmedabad%20leg%20of%20the%20trial%20is%20set%20to%20continue%20for%20another%20year%2C%20with%20researchers%20closely%20monitoring%20its%20long-term%20impact%20on%20indoor%20temperatures%20and%20overall%20well-being.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20Mahila%20Housing%20Trust%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20been%20addressing%20climate%20change%20effects%20since%202010%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fem%3Eexplains%20Vadgama%3Cem%3E.%20%E2%80%9COur%20approach%20focuses%20on%20five%20key%20stresses%3A%20air%20pollution%2C%20water%20scarcity%2C%20flooding%2C%20heat%20stress%2C%20and%20vector-borne%20diseases.%20Cool%20roof%20technology%20is%20our%20primary%20solution%20for%20heat%20stress%2C%20targeting%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20communities.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fem%3EShe%20emphasizes%20that%20these%20interventions%20are%20critical%20for%20slum%20dwellings%20that%20are%3Cem%3E%20%E2%80%9Ccongested%20with%20limited%20space%E2%80%9D%20and%20typically%20covered%20with%20%E2%80%9Cstructurally%20weak%20tin%20or%20asbestos%20cement%20sheets%20that%20absorb%20tremendous%20heat.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20are%20some%20of%20the%20challenges%20with%20implementing%20this%20programme%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20proven%20benefits%2C%20several%20practical%20challenges%20exist%20in%20implementation.%20Despite%20its%20promise%2C%20cool%20roof%20adoption%20faces%20roadblocks%E2%80%94from%20technical%20skills%20and%20weak%20rooftops%20to%20deeper%20gender%20barriers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWomen%20are%20most%20affected%20by%20indoor%20heat%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vadgama%2C%20%E2%80%9Cyet%20they%20often%20don%E2%80%99t%20control%20household%20budgets%20to%20approve%20application%20costs%E2%80%94even%20when%20they%20see%20the%20value.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStructural%20concerns%20present%20another%20barrier%2C%20especially%20in%20informal%20settlements%20where%20many%20roofs%20are%20ageing%20or%20rusty%2C%20creating%20uncertainty%20about%20whether%20the%20paint%20will%20adhere%20properly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20important%20gender%20dimension%20also%20affects%20adoption%20rates.%20Women%20experience%20the%20greatest%20impact%20from%20extreme%20indoor%20heat%20since%20they%20typically%20remain%20in%20these%20homes%20throughout%20the%20day%20for%20domestic%20and%20livelihood%20activities%20yet%20often%20lack%20financial%20decision-making%20authority%20within%20households.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20many%20cases%2C%20women%20recognise%20the%20value%20of%20cool%20roof%20technology%20and%20even%20purchase%20the%20paint%C2%A0%20but%20cannot%20secure%20approval%20for%20the%20additional%20application%20expenses.%20This%20gender%20dynamic%20significantly%20hampers%20adoption%20in%20the%20very%20households%20that%20would%20benefit%20most%20from%20the%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20the%20Solar%20Reflective%20White%20Paint%20technology%20to%20reach%20its%20full%20potential%2C%20we%20need%20to%20address%20two%20key%20challenges%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fem%3Esuggests%20Vadgama%3Cem%3E.%20%E2%80%9CFirst%20is%20awareness%E2%80%94many%20people%20simply%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20this%20affordable%20solution%20exists.%20Second%20is%20policy%20integration.%20Every%20city%20in%20Ahmedabad%20already%20has%20a%20heat%20action%20plan.%20These%20plans%20should%20be%20expanded%20to%20include%20cool%20roof%20implementation%20at%20both%20residential%20and%20institutional%20levels%2C%20covering%20homes%20as%20well%20as%20public%20facilities%20like%20healthcare%20centers%2C%20Anganwadis%2C%20schools%2C%20and%20transportation%20hubs.%20This%20comprehensive%20approach%20would%20significantly%20amplify%20our%20impact.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Funnamed-2_11zon-1746953145-500x750.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22From%20Ahmedabad%20to%20global%20trials%2C%20Cool%20Roofs%20are%20now%20a%20key%20tool%20in%20fighting%20rising%20urban%20heat.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Funnamed-2_11zon-1746953145-500x750.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Funnamed-2_11zon-1746953145-200x300.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Funnamed-2_11zon-1746953145-768x1152.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Funnamed-2_11zon-1746953145-150x225.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Funnamed-2_11zon-1746953145.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-426849%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22750%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFrom%20Ahmedabad%20to%20global%20trials%2C%20Cool%20Roofs%20are%20now%20a%20key%20tool%20in%20fighting%20rising%20urban%20heat.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECool%20Bus%20Stops%3A%20Another%20innovation%20with%20potential%20to%20beat%20the%20heat%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20innovative%20initiative%20aimed%20at%20combating%20rising%20temperatures%20in%20Ahmedabad%20is%20the%20%3Cem%3ECool%20Bus%20Stop%3C%2Fem%3E%20project.%20Launched%20on%208th%20March%202025%2C%20this%20pilot%20was%20introduced%20at%20Lal%20Darwaja%E2%80%94a%20bustling%20local%20market%20area%E2%80%94by%20the%20Ahmedabad%20Municipal%20Corporation%20and%20Ahmedabad%20Municipal%20Transport%20Service%20(AMTS)%2C%20with%20support%20from%20the%20Mahila%20Housing%20Trust%20(MHT).%20The%20goal%20is%20to%20provide%20much-needed%20comfort%20and%20relief%20to%20daily%20commuters%20while%20they%20wait%20for%20buses%20in%20the%20scorching%20heat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3ECool%20Bus%20Stop%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20designed%20using%20climate-responsive%20materials%20and%20tools%20that%20help%20create%20a%20significantly%20cooler%20micro-environment.%20At%20the%20heart%20of%20this%20setup%20is%20an%20energy-efficient%2C%20high-pressure%20misting%20system.%20It%20releases%20ultra-fine%20mist%20particles%20that%20evaporate%20quickly%2C%20reducing%20the%20ambient%20temperature%20within%20the%20bus%20stop.%20This%20offers%20immediate%20relief%20to%20waiting%20passengers%20and%20introduces%20a%20more%20humane%20and%20climate-conscious%20approach%20to%20everyday%20public%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-86_11zon-1746955760.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Khus%20curtains%20and%20misting%20systems%20turn%20this%20Ahmedabad%20bus%20stop%20into%20a%20heat-safe%20haven%20for%20daily%20commuters.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-86_11zon-1746955760.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-86_11zon-1746955760-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-86_11zon-1746955760-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-86_11zon-1746955760-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-86_11zon-1746955760-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-426850%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKhus%20curtains%20and%20misting%20systems%20turn%20this%20Ahmedabad%20bus%20stop%20into%20a%20heat-safe%20haven%20for%20daily%20commuters.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20innovation%20uses%20a%20high-pressure%20misting%20system%20that%20creates%20a%20cooling%20effect%20through%20evaporation.%3Cem%3E%20%E2%80%9CThe%20water%20is%20pumped%20out%20of%20the%20nozzle%20at%20a%20pressure%20of%200.2%20microns.%20The%20particle%20breaks%20at%20a%20pressure%20of%205%20to%2015%20microns%20and%20creates%20fogging%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fem%3Eexplains%20Dipika.%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3EShe%20adds%20that%20the%20cool%20bus%20stops%20particularly%20benefit%3Cem%3E%20%E2%80%9Cpeople%20like%20senior%20citizens%20who%20have%20dehydration%20problems%20and%20daily%20wage%20workers%20who%20do%20a%20lot%20of%20physical%20work.%20If%20they%20get%20some%20comfort%2C%20it%20has%20a%20positive%20impact%20on%20their%20body%20and%20mind.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20innovation%20uses%20less%20energy%20than%20traditional%20air%20cooling%20conditioners%2C%20which%20have%20features%20such%20as%20timers%20and%20adjustable%20pressure.%20It%20also%20ensures%20dust%20suppression%20and%20uses%20khus%20curtains%20to%20ensure%20natural%20cooling%20and%20act%20as%20a%20barrier%20between%20the%20hot%20and%20cool%20air.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20scale%20of%20impact%20is%20remarkable%2C%E2%80%9D%20notes%20Vadgama.%20%E2%80%9COver%20a%20single%20season%2C%20more%20than%206%20lakh%20commuters%20will%20benefit%20from%20this%20cooling%20technology.%20When%20you%20calculate%20the%20cost%20per%20person%20served%2C%20it%20emerges%20as%20an%20exceptionally%20economical%20intervention%20for%20heat%20mitigation%20in%20public%20spaces.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20of%20Cool%20Bus%20Stops%20has%20been%20tremendous.%20The%20Cool%20Bus%20Stop%20consistently%20recorded%20temperatures%205%E2%80%937%20degrees%20lower%20than%20regular%20bus%20stops.%20The%20highest%20temperature%20difference%20of%206.8%20degrees%20was%20observed%20on%2030th%20March%2C%20showcasing%20substantial%20heat%20mitigation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20shaded%20area%20will%20provide%20cool%20air%20and%20bring%20relief%20to%20people%20during%20the%20summer.%20It%20will%20help%20protect%20them%20from%20heatstroke%20and%20other%20heat-related%20illnesses.%20I%20sincerely%20congratulate%20the%20AMC%2C%20AMTS%2C%20Mahila%20Housing%20Trust%2C%20and%20the%20entire%20team%20for%20this%20initiative.%20I%20hope%20similar%20technology%20will%20be%20implemented%20on%20other%20platforms%20in%20the%20future%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%20said%20Shri%20Pratibhaben%20Jain%2C%20Mayor%2C%20Ahmedabad%2C%20on%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20Cool%20Bus%20Stop.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20very%20relaxing%20for%20the%20poor%20people%20like%20us.%20We%20are%20mason%20labors%2C%20and%20using%20this%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3Ebus-stop%20regularly%20in%20the%20summer.%20We%20have%20never%20seen%20such%20a%20thing.%20This%20kind%20of%20facility%20is%20really%20good%20for%20the%20people%20like%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%20said%20a%20woman%20daily%20wage%20labourer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20first-of-its-kind%20%E2%80%98Cool%20Bus%20Stop%E2%80%99%20marks%20a%20significant%20step%20towards%20climate%20resilience%20in%20Ahmedabad.%20By%20improving%20comfort%20in%20public%20spaces%2C%20this%20initiative%20sets%20an%20example%20for%20other%20cities%20in%20India%20to%20prioritise%20public%20health%20and%20well-being%20in%20the%20face%20of%20rising%20temperatures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201536px)%20100vw%2C%201536px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Fbanner-1746776121.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D